    <item>
      <title>继芝加哥之后，特朗普移民政策打击目标转向纽约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/ice-expands-focus-to-new-york-city-after-chicago-raids</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国移民和海关执法局周日抵达芝加哥后，又在布朗克斯进行了一次高调行动，新任国土安全部部长克里斯蒂·诺姆也参与其中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/ice-expands-focus-to-new-york-city-after-chicago-raids</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 14:33:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗伯特·肯尼迪在参议院听证会前表示他并不反对疫苗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/rfk-jr-walks-back-vaccine-rhetoric-before-hhs-senate-hearings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗伯特·F·肯尼迪 (Robert F. Kennedy Jr.) 是唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 总统提名的美国卫生与公众服务部部长，他本周将告诉参议员，他并不“反对疫苗或反对产业”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/rfk-jr-walks-back-vaccine-rhetoric-before-hhs-senate-hearings</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹麦领导人争取欧洲支持解决格陵兰僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/danish-premier-starts-whirlwind-tour-for-support-over-greenland</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦首相梅特·弗雷德里克森寻求争取欧洲盟友的支持，以抵制唐纳德·特朗普侵占格陵兰岛的行为，她试图展现团结，同时避免激怒美国总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/danish-premier-starts-whirlwind-tour-for-support-over-greenland</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 07:00:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄亥俄州新兴城市利用市政债券进行 10 亿美元机场改造</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/ohio-boomtown-turns-to-munis-for-1-billion-to-revamp-airport</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄亥俄州哥伦布市正处于繁荣时期。但随着越来越多的企业和居民涌向该州首府，以享受更便宜的生活成本，该州老化的机场正面临压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/ohio-boomtown-turns-to-munis-for-1-billion-to-revamp-airport</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 18:57:31 GMT</pubDate>
